metadata.name: User Onboarding & Education Burrow #1/10
metadata.description:
The dYdX Foundation is fostering a movement for advanced traders. Becoming an Ambassador means adopting decentralized and permissionless technology. 

Through these means we will achieve financial self-sovereignty, security, and prosperity. Our vision is to push the dYdX protocol forwards toward community-led growth, development, and self-sustainability, through education, media, and culture. 

This NFT grants access to the User Onboarding & Education Burrow on the Clarity Application.
